name: Life of an artist (No bullshit.)
description:
It's a GIF. Dimension is 1x1
"So where do I start? Right. I work in the same boring room and it's so freaking dull.
Why don't I decorate? I'm saving for something I can only afford as a poster on the wall.
My life is so god damn dull I have to put all the colorful stuffs on my works."
